I'm so sorry you need to believe that.

732
00:48:09,820 --> 00:48:10,690
你想要吗
Do you want it?

733
00:48:10,950 --> 00:48:12,940
了解你的人  只剩下我了  克莱尔
I'm the only one left who knows you, Claire.

